{"tid":1119700,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"認真曼聯如果係香港開公司，我一定定仆去做","createTime":"2019-04-22T06:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T07:48:29.000Z","uid":1823,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"25b6b6d7d9aad7fede2a917087e53d022f8b731f","tid":1119700,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:30:28.000Z","msg":"首先人工方面，不論才能，比同行平均水平高(山神50k)，甚至新仔/能力唔出眾都同其他公司骨幹成員一樣人工(shaw同vvd一樣週薪)<br />\n<br />\n其次福利方面，容許員工成日請病假，實際工作時間低都唔會被炒(鐘斯成日傷都可以續約)<br />\n<br />\n最後同事之間有良好合作關係，對上司嘅工作指示有咩唔滿意，同大老闆講聲就可以換上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衰就衰在山頭文化比較嚴重，不過識埋堆就可以了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7228010b2426c7f5e94cb055099454130fa34dfb","tid":1119700,"uid":153,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:32:09.000Z","msg":"返工鍾意著咩都得 話之你個頭鬼五馬六(普巴)"},{"pid":"4089a702d09db0d7b18aa16ed2dfd3b0c788afcf","tid":1119700,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7228010b2426c7f5e94cb055099454130fa34dfb","tid":1119700,"uid":153,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:32:09.000Z","msg":"返工鍾意著咩都得 話之你個頭鬼五馬六(普巴)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"可以日日換髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0446ac9cc7eced7cc1f43668259fc2d17310516","tid":1119700,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"shaw依條友出波都未識  同vvd同薪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190f37a9ac6660a5c1622e6d112788b815f4cc7b","tid":1119700,"uid":217643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"好似唔洗翻工添（什麼是練波？）"},{"pid":"ae4cb2c6c8fe14f0ca795841